</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Changes in Electronic Health Record Use Time and Documentation over the Course of a Decade</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Goldstein%20IH"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Isaac H Goldstein</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Isaac H Goldstein</span>, <span class="degrees">BA</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Ophthalmology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Goldstein%20IH"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Isaac H Goldstein</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hwang%20T"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Thomas Hwang</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Thomas Hwang</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Ophthalmology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
