</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Gowrisankaran%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Sowjanya Gowrisankaran</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Sowjanya Gowrisankaran</span>, <span class="degrees">PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Medical Informatics and Clinical Epidemiology, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Gowrisankaran%20S"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Sowjanya Gowrisankaran</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Bales%20R"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Ryan Bales</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Ryan Bales</span>, <span class="degrees">BA</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Ophthalmology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Bales%20R"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Ryan Bales</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chiang%20MF"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Michael F Chiang</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Michael F Chiang</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Ophthalmology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Medical Informatics and Clinical Epidemiology, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chiang%20MF"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Michael F Chiang</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hribar%20MR"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id6"><span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id6">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span>, <span class="degrees">PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Medical Informatics and Clinical Epidemiology, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hribar%20MR"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="anp_a" aria-expanded="false">Article notes</button></li>
