<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="A1">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Ophthalmology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div id="A2">
<sup>2</sup>Department of Medical Informatics and Clinical Epidemiology, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, Oregon.</div>
<div class="author-notes p">
<div class="fn" id="FN1">
<p id="P1">Author Contributions:</p>
<p id="P2">Conception and design: Goldstein, Hwang, Chiang, Hribar</p>
<p id="P3">Analysis and interpretation: Goldstein, Hwang, Gowrisankaran, Bales, Chiang, Hribar</p>
<p id="P4">Data collection: Goldstein, Bales, Chiang, Hribar</p>
<p id="P5">Obtained funding: Hribar, Chiang</p>
